body.body: Semi or fully synthetic 10W/40 or 10W/50 engine oil which meets specification API SH (or higher) and JASO MA. Triumph recommends Castrol Power 1 Racing 4T 10W/40 or 10W/50 (fully synthetic) engine oil, sold as Castrol Power RS Racing 4T 10W/40 or 10W/50 (fully synthetic) in some countries. Refer to the Lubrication chapter in the Service Manual
3.30 litres (oil and filter change). Always refer to the check sight glass for the correct level
Lubricate the seals for the camshaft cover bolts with a proprietary temporary rubber lubricant (at the factory P-80Â® is used)
Tighten the camshaft cover bolts in the sequence shown below.
Chain spray suitable for O-ring chains
Chain spray suitable for O-ring chains
Must not exceed 0.8A (refer to the Service Manual)
For current parts information, refer to the Electronic Parts Catalogue.
